    <h1>Algorithmic Penalty</h1>
    <p class="description">An automatic ranking demotion applied by Google when a site trips a quality algorithm. <strong>No notification</strong>, no reconsideration request — recovery waits for the next update cycle.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
